<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.6">
<l>mattaḷaṅ koṭṭa varicaṅkam niṉṟūta</l>
<l>muttuṭait tāmanirai tāḻnta pantaṟkīḻ</l>
<l>maittuṉa ṉampi matucūtaṉ vanteṉṉaik</l>
<l>kaittalam paṟṟak kaṉākkaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that [my] cross-cousin, the great [Lord], Madhusūdana came</l>
<l>beneath the pandal from which rows of strands of pearls hung</l>
<l>[and] held held me by the palm</l>
<l>as drums were beaten and conches were blown unceasingly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
